companyInfo.introduction: Cng ty C phn PVI (PVI) c tin thn lTng cng ty c phn Bo him Du kh Vit Namc thnh lp vo nm1996. Cng ty hot ng trong lnh vc kinh doanhbo him v u t ti chnh. T nm 2006, PVI chuyn sang hot ng theo m hnh Tng cng ty c phn. Hin ti, PVI ng th hai v th phn trn th trng bo him phi nhn th Vit Nam v tip tc gi vng v tr ng u lnh vc bo him cng nghip trong nc v c mi quan h tt p vi cc ch tu ln nh: VSP, PTSC, Vitranschart, Vosco, Vinashin. Hin nay, PVI l doanh nghip bo him duy nht  Vit Nam c hp ng bo him c nh nng lng ti th trng Lloyds v cc hp ng bo him c nh hng hi, phi hng hi. Ngoi ra, PVI cn m rng th trng nhn ti bo him ra cc nc khu vc v th gii vi i tc ca l nhng nh bo him, ti bo him hng u trn th gii v khu vc nh Swiss Re, Munich Re, Korean Re.
